00:17:56.650 --> 00:18:00.130
where local music is
locked in to community life

00:18:00.130 --> 00:18:03.420
and community memory too.

00:18:03.420 --> 00:18:08.460
So it really is a kind of paradise
for someone of my interests.

00:18:08.460 --> 00:18:12.860
It's a place where people
come together around music.

00:18:12.860 --> 00:18:16.530
It's a place where music is part of
a glue that holds people together

00:18:16.530 --> 00:18:21.960
in the community, connects them to
each other as well as to a sense

00:18:21.960 --> 00:18:25.380
of the past that's still
very present there too.

00:18:25.380 --> 00:18:28.250
Now it's not an easy place.

00:18:28.250 --> 00:18:31.420
