00:18:37.880 --> 00:18:41.380
And the economy has really
been bad for decades.

00:18:41.380 --> 00:18:44.100
High unemployment.

00:18:44.100 --> 00:18:46.910
Significant out migration.

00:18:46.910 --> 00:18:49.050
