00:19:03.050 --> 00:19:05.400
Seem to go to western Canada too.

00:19:05.400 --> 00:19:11.250 position:56%
But, you know, the interesting thing
is survey after survey there shows

00:19:11.250 --> 00:19:15.410
that people who stay talk about
how satisfied they are with life,

00:19:15.410 --> 00:19:20.120
that there's a kind of unusually
high degree of satisfaction

00:19:20.120 --> 00:19:24.010
with life in this place
where things are not so easy.

00:19:24.010 --> 00:19:29.180
So, you know, I have done some
thinking about how to think

00:19:29.180 --> 00:19:31.810
about this and what to call it.

00:19:31.810 --> 00:19:35.790
And I want to talk a
little bit about that too.

00:19:35.790 --> 00:19:41.660
I kept thinking there about how
integral the music is to life.

00:19:41.660 --> 00:19:45.760
And to a sort of understanding
