00:24:42.590 --> 00:24:48.460
So as part of this maintaining what
the community values we see the

00:24:48.460 --> 00:24:51.950
development of institutions
and venues and so forth,

00:24:51.950 --> 00:24:55.920
including what you see here, the
Celtic Music Interpretive Center

00:24:55.920 --> 00:24:58.440
and the small community
